title: Personal Portfolio
description: My personal porfolio, highlighting a bit about myself, my projects, my resume, and how to contact me!

title: OCD Comorbidity Analysis
description: This project uses a synthetic dataset of 1,500 simulated OCD patients to explore potential patterns and relationships between demographic factors and OCD comorbidities. It focuses on exploratory data analysis (EDA) and baseline predictive modeling.
